with version stable 1.10 1.9
with base    clamav
with elect   postfix '' '' SMTP daemon
with role    network/email security/anti-virus
with trait   console server
with source  http://memberwebs.com/nielsen/software/clamsmtp/clamsmtp-$VERSION.tar.gz
with info    good 20120604
with info    home http://memberwebs.com/nielsen/software/clamsmtp/
with info    cite 'SMTP filter that checks for viruses using ClamAV
It aims to be lightweight, reliable, and simple.'

build(){
default_build &&
mkdir  -pvm 755 $DESTDIR/etc &&
install -vm 644 doc/clamsmtpd.conf $DESTDIR/etc
}
